article_title: Congress sends health law repeal to Obama for first time
article_text:
By Erica Werner, The Associated Press

Posted Jan. 6, 2016 at 12:01 AM

Updated Jan 7, 2016 at 3:46 AM

article_metadata.description: WASHINGTON (AP) " The GOP-led Congress sent legislation to President Barack Obama Wednesday repealing his signature health law, fulfilling a promise to Republican voters in a presidential election year but inviting a certain veto.
article_metadata.author: Erica Werner, The Associated Press
